Peru Consumer Credit Demand ‘Vigorous’ in August, Velarde Says

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-09-16T17:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/peru-consumer-credit-demand-vigorous-in-august-velarde-says.html
Demand for  consumer credit  in  Peru 
was “vigorous” in August, central bank President Julio Velarde
said in a presentation in  Lima  today.  While the credit market is picking up, inflation will
remain below 0.2 percent a month, he said, adding that there
were no signs of inflationary pressures.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Quigley in Lima at 
 jquigley8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net  